There are both Linux and Windows version of the app.

To execute the application you will need:
  OpenGL (probably already installed)
  Freeglut 3.0
    Linux:   package freeglut3 (on Debian)
    Windows: library freeglut.dll

The library freeglut.dll for windows can be obtained from
http://www.transmissionzero.co.uk/software/freeglut-devel/
as freeglut 3.0.0 MinGW Package.


See COPYING for full text of GNU General Public Licence version 3

A brief documentation of the application can be obtained by typing :help in it.
Default settings can be read directly from geometric_figures.conf.

Other information (like Czech user_guide) and source code can be found on my web page
  http://ondracek-lukas.hys.cz/projects .


If you want to support the development of this application,
you can send a donation to my PayPal account <ondracek.lukas@gmail.com>.
